{"tid":2355631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：對香港大圍捕承認政治責任 強調普通市民只要不反共則不受影響","createTime":"2021-01-06T08:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T20:21:07.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7cae9df9875ada16530081532fad3bba2c04d9ca","tid":2355631,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"外交部：支持香港警方依法履職 布林肯表達關注<br />\n<br />\n多名曾參與去年7月民主派35+初選的民主派人士，今早被警方上門拘捕。在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，支持香港警方依法履職，強調中國是法治國家，香港是法治社會，香港市民享有的權利和自由並無受到任何影響，只有一些外部勢力和香港個別人士，相互勾結，企圖破壞中國穩定和安全的自由，才受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2373614&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=fa134646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373614</a>"},{"pid":"b433e715f630b583fd59163a1dd7369d16cea1f2","tid":2355631,"uid":146621,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"唔可以反對<br />\n即係冇自由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c094170350a15eed7c2e61c2eef8e980c7a2a73","tid":2355631,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b433e715f630b583fd59163a1dd7369d16cea1f2","tid":2355631,"uid":146621,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"唔可以反對<br />\n即係冇自由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:37:33.000Z","msg":"放心,佢地一定話捉異見者即係代表有自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac83b4304c25caf6781a2f87d0d98932c09ad04","tid":2355631,"uid":8308,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b433e715f630b583fd59163a1dd7369d16cea1f2","tid":2355631,"uid":146621,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"唔可以反對<br />\n即係冇自由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class